    <p class="card-text">Key takeaways:</p>
    <p class="card-text">Frame analysis (Wireshark) and simulation (Packet Tracer) are essential for transforming raw data into a reliable architecture. </p>
    <p class="card-text"> Accurate technical documentation is the key to ensuring maintenance and future evolution of the IT infrastructure.</p>
    <p class="card-text"> Access protection (SSH) and flow isolation via VLANs are absolute priorities for securing the company.</p>
    <p class="card-text"> Autonomy when facing failures, such as configuring the firewall for the TFTP service, is crucial to ensuring service availability.</p>
